processingCommand.script:
!---Example AE Script with Shell Task----


:S &response# = '${response}'
:S &actual_start_time# = JSON_GET_VALUE(&response#, $.actual_start_time)
:S &actual_end_time# = JSON_GET_VALUE(&response#, $.actual_end_time)

:P "$&actual_start_time#:   &actual_start_time#"
:P "$&actual_end_time#:     &actual_end_time#" 


echo ${actual_start_time}
echo ${actual_end_time}
